# DataAttributes

Convenience helpers to provide [HTML data attributes](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Use_data_attributes)
from model to view.

## Setup

Just add this into your `Gemfile`:

```ruby
gem 'data_attributes'
```

Then, just run a `bundle install`.

